  ./COVERAGE.md:1040:| `org.fusesource.hawtjni:hawtjni-runtime` | [1.9<br>- 1.12](metadata/org.fusesource.hawtjni/hawtjni-runtime/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> HawtJNI Runtime provides the annotations and helper API that projects using HawtJNI compile against. It includes the runtime classes used to describe JNI bindings and load bundled native libraries from Java.</details> | [100.0% (2/2 calls)](stats/org.fusesource.hawtjni/hawtjni-runtime/) |
